This may be due to incomplete or inaccurate information, or the details not suiting the basic expectations of the job role, or other factors.
We appreciate your time and effort and wish you the best in your job search.
Regards,
Aishwarya Kesavan
HR Executive - AVASOFT
Alpha City (SSPDL), 3rd Floor | Beta Block, Navalur | CH – 600 130
www.avasoft.com (http://www.avasoft.com/)

Dear Student,

I hope you are doing well!

We are excited to offer you an incredible opportunity to join us as a Campus Ambassador in collaboration with Microsoft & Wipro DICE ID. This is your chance to represent Wayspire EdTech Pvt. Ltd., promote career-enhancing programs on your campus, and gain invaluable experience.

As a Campus Ambassador, you’ll benefit from:

An Internship Certificate upon successful completion.
Opportunities for a Pre-Placement Offer (PPO).
A Letter of Recommendation (LOR) to boost your academic and professional profile.
A Stipend of up to ₹25,000, based on performance.
Enhanced leadership and communication skills.
Exclusive rewards and networking opportunities with industry experts.
To get started, kindly fill out this Google Form to express your interest and provide your details:
Form Link: https://forms.gle/uZcu7TCuNU4ytZti7

We look forward to collaborating with you and empowering students on your campus with world-class career-building opportunities.

Feel free to reply to this email if you have any questions. We’re here to help!

Thanks & Regards

Sumit Singh
Business Development Associate
Wayspire Ed Tech Pvt. Ltd.
M: +91 92668 00475
E: sumit@wayspire.in
